  "body": "**Is this a BUG REPORT or FEATURE REQUEST?**:\r\n\r\n/kind feature\r\n\r\nThis is a ScaleIO plugin volume feature to do the following:\r\n- Reads node label `scaleio.sdcGuid` value for the SDC GUID\r\n- Uses value to look up the Scaleio SDC `instance ID`\r\n- If label not found, falls back to current way of doing instance id look up now\r\n\r\nThis enhancement allows the ScaleIO plugin to work properly work even if the drv_cfg binary is not installed on the kubelet node.",
